Package: lrun
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libseccomp2 (>= 2.0)
Description: Run programs on Linux with resources limited.
 lrun can be used to start a process with resources (ex. time, memory, network,
 device, syscall, etc.) limited, in an easy way.
